 if, in the future, everything breaks humanity=E2=80=99s way? Each episode =
has a companion story, generated by GPT-4, which will serve as a jumping-of=
f point for a hopeful, speculative discussion about what humanity could pos=
sibly get right if we leverage technology=E2=80=94and our collective effort=
=E2=80=94effectively.
